<section class="hero section-shell" id="home" data-section="home">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow-index">SYS.00</span>
        <span>SYSTEMS / BAD IDEAS / CONTROLLED CONDITIONS</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="reveal" data-reveal>
        I keep following<br />
        the signal<br />
        <em>down.</em>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-lede reveal" data-reveal>
        Andrew. I build systems, break them on purpose, and occasionally write down
        why. Mostly Rust, distributed compute, model infrastructure, security labs,
        and projects that would be easier to explain if I enjoyed elevator pitches.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions reveal" data-reveal>
        <a class="button button--primary" href="#work">
          <span>SEE_WHAT_BROKE</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">↘</span>
